description: This Chainlink VRF top 2% rating Cooter purrs with a rating of 89, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 267, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, 3 for East, 5 for South, and 8 for West. Cooter has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/90893-73582-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Cooter [267 Votes, Top 2% Rating]
